########################################################################
# Symptom → Disease (indicatesDisease) Relations
########################################################################

cds:Headache            cds:indicatesDisease cds:Hypertension , cds:Migraine .
cds:Dizziness           cds:indicatesDisease cds:Hypertension .
cds:Hypertension_Symptom cds:indicatesDisease cds:Hypertension .
cds:Fever               cds:indicatesDisease cds:Pneumonia , cds:Tonsillitis .
cds:Cough               cds:indicatesDisease cds:Pneumonia .
cds:ShortnessOfBreath   cds:indicatesDisease cds:Pneumonia , cds:CoronaryArteryDisease .
cds:Fatigue             cds:indicatesDisease cds:Type2Diabetes .
cds:FrequentUrination   cds:indicatesDisease cds:Type2Diabetes .
cds:BlurredVision       cds:indicatesDisease cds:Type2Diabetes .
cds:ChestPain           cds:indicatesDisease cds:CoronaryArteryDisease .
cds:Rash                cds:indicatesDisease cds:AllergicReaction .
cds:Itching             cds:indicatesDisease cds:AllergicReaction .
cds:JointPain           cds:indicatesDisease cds:RheumatoidArthritis .
cds:Swelling            cds:indicatesDisease cds:RheumatoidArthritis .
cds:Nausea              cds:indicatesDisease cds:Migraine , cds:Appendicitis .
cds:AbdominalPain       cds:indicatesDisease cds:Appendicitis .
cds:Vomiting            cds:indicatesDisease cds:Appendicitis .
cds:SoreThroat          cds:indicatesDisease cds:Tonsillitis .
cds:Anxiety             cds:indicatesDisease cds:AnxietyDisorder .
cds:Insomnia            cds:indicatesDisease cds:AnxietyDisorder .


########################################################################
# Disease → Disease (isRelatedConditionOf) — Transitive chain
# Reasoner infers: Hypertension isRelatedConditionOf HeartFailure
########################################################################

cds:Hypertension          cds:isRelatedConditionOf cds:CoronaryArteryDisease .
cds:CoronaryArteryDisease cds:isRelatedConditionOf cds:HeartFailure .
